{
  "2124500": {
    "name": "Forlorn Memories",
    "steam_appid": 2124500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/48be8d439279f3b8e52d8945f0d8fe6d.avif?t=1770220532\" width=620 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/f04d54fe3cc2100ec90ddd8c77a2e6ea.avif?t=1770220532\" width=600 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Forlorn Memories</strong> is a story-driven, old-school inspired 3D steampunk fantasy RPG with monster catching and life/dating sim elements, where your choices shape the world and its inhabitants. Some consequences are immediate, others only reveal themselves as your journey unfolds, leading to different endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What you do with the life you’ve been given is up to you. You can chase your lost memories no matter the cost, or choose a cozier path, finding love, friendship, and letting the world move on. No choice is the wrong one.<br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/2f34f2ef884c7a4f85ad1b35dc7cf472.webp?t=1770220532\" width=25 height=24 /></span>  <i>“Memories are fleeting - what are you willing to sacrifice to remember?” </i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/2f34f2ef884c7a4f85ad1b35dc7cf472.webp?t=1770220532\" width=25 height=24 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/a06bccd9cd0fea9a0597babbf45f28df.avif?t=1770220532\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/e5349931dbca4a61ac296e1a5ffc3fec.avif?t=1770220532\" width=600 height=110 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/e64946eb0a49ccb146acdf0be666e039.avif?t=1770220532\" width=600 height=767 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/0fc8a884a5520f8c29ef6387fde09d20.avif?t=1770220532\" width=600 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/a162fa5e79c382a503b1f2fd6eb5ef3a.webp?t=1770220532\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/286ae16af382714224f361d34ac320c8.avif?t=1770220532\" width=500 height=92 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/ad092898f908a409fecd5672b9579e07.webp?t=1770220532\" width=34 height=34 /></span>  Will you play as Gavin or Aria? <strong> </strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/276d3b8d288589690340126b4d3579b1.webp?t=1770220532\" width=34 height=34 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Strangely, both carry the same emptiness within them: missing memories, and for some time now, they’ve been trying to recover their past lives and uncover the truth behind it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Neither protagonist is a silent character. Gavin and Aria have their own voices, react to events, and actively comment on what’s happening around them. Each has a distinct personality and backstory, yet you can rename and fully customize them so the character still feels like your own. And the protagonist you don’t choose doesn’t disappear, they remain part of the world, and may even cross paths with you later… or join your journey.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/da491c434d95d38d54afa80fb0b55bbe.poster.avif?t=1770220532\" width=700 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/da491c434d95d38d54afa80fb0b55bbe.webm?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/da491c434d95d38d54afa80fb0b55bbe.mp4?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/b873f29bc8bfcab3ccf22227a316e93c.poster.avif?t=1770220532\" width=700 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/b873f29bc8bfcab3ccf22227a316e93c.webm?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/b873f29bc8bfcab3ccf22227a316e93c.mp4?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/36cb08aab00b2e46e306cc0fb22b2a81.avif?t=1770220532\" width=500 height=92 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <strong>Forlorn Memories</strong> features a cast of <strong>playable characters</strong> — potential party members who can <strong>optionally</strong> join you if your goals align, you earn their trust, or you convince them in your own way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Along the journey, you’ll also meet a variety of <strong>non-playable characters</strong>. Every character has their own <strong>backstory, personality, goals, dreams, class, hobbies, and daily routine.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/be73c1235a8db789d51915eb27c9c5c3.poster.avif?t=1770220532\" width=42 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/be73c1235a8db789d51915eb27c9c5c3.webm?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/0c75e0d80927b796f009a503f1addb1f.poster.avif?t=1770220532\" width=43 height=85 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/0c75e0d80927b796f009a503f1addb1f.webm?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/dc551f2bc333b73d81cd5e83a699d5a6.poster.avif?t=1770220532\" width=51 height=93 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/dc551f2bc333b73d81cd5e83a699d5a6.webm?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/6461b654c66aa6afecf80d0befda687d.poster.avif?t=1770220532\" width=44 height=86 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/6461b654c66aa6afecf80d0befda687d.webm?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/6461b654c66aa6afecf80d0befda687d.mp4?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/de2af18cb0e21ea175c357acfff2ebd2.poster.avif?t=1770220532\" width=44 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/de2af18cb0e21ea175c357acfff2ebd2.webm?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/de2af18cb0e21ea175c357acfff2ebd2.mp4?t=1770220532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124500/extras/2f9